            <sentence>
                <offset>1136</offset>
                <text>In the past, the chromosomal analysis in peripheral blood lymphocytes had revealed a 46,XY(90%)/47,XYY(10%) mosaic.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>1252</offset>
                <text>Molecular analysis revealed a missense mutation in exon 3 (614 G&gt;T) that causes a change in the residue 205 from Ser to Ile.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>1377</offset>
                <text>The same mutation was found in his mother and in her three sisters, who have mild phenotypical signs (hypertelorism, widow's peak).</text>
            </sentence>
